Author: vineet21
Title: High Shipping Costs Leading To High Shopping Cart Abandonment
Content:
According to a survey by web measurement firm comScore Inc. for PayPal, the online payment service owned by eBay Inc.,
"Shipping costs is the reason behind a lot of online consumers adding items to a shopping cart but leaving before completing the purchase."
